'''保羅·黑門'''（{{lang-en|'''Paul Heyman'''}}，{{bd|1965年|9月11日|catIdx=M}}），是美國娛樂業的製片人、作家、表演者、營銷商、推廣者、[[職業摔角|職業摔角]][[經紀人|經紀人]]和評論員。目前受聘於[[世界摔角娛樂|世界摔角娛樂]]（WWE），並在[[SmackDown_LIVE|SmackDown]]品牌上亮相。他幾十年來迴避了“經紀人”的標籤，而更喜歡“擁護者”或“代理人”一詞。<ref name="OWOW">{{cite web|url=http://www.onlineworldofwrestling.com/bios/p/paul-heyman/|title=Paul Heyman Profile|accessdate=2020-06-12|publisher=Online World of Wrestling|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007094211/http://www.onlineworldofwrestling.com/bios/p/paul-heyman/|archive-date=2012-10-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

黑門也是世界摔角娛樂收購[[極限冠軍摔角|極限冠軍摔角]]後至其解散前，極限冠軍摔角的[[負責人|負責人]]。

在WWE期間，黑門目前擔任著[[羅曼·瑞恩斯|羅曼·瑞恩斯]]的經紀人，他也曾與多位重量級職業摔角選手簽約，如：[[CM_Punk|CM Punk]]、[[羅伯·凡·達姆|羅伯·凡·達姆]]、[[冷石·史蒂夫·奧斯汀|冷石·史蒂夫·奧斯汀]]、[[寇特·安格|寇特·安格]]、[[Big_Show|Big Show]]、[[雷·密斯特里歐|雷·密斯特里歐]]、[[送葬者_(摔角手)|送葬者]]及[[布洛克·雷斯納|布洛克·雷斯納]]等。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Arda|first1=Ocal|title=New 'Paul Heyman Guy' revealed, Triple H wobbly on Raw|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2013-05-21/sports/bal-new-paul-heyman-guy-revealed-triple-h-wobbly-on-raw-20130520_1_big-e-langston-extreme-rules-triple-h|work=[[The_Baltimore_Sun|The Baltimore Sun]]|accessdate=2020-06-12|language=en|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402111734/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2013-05-21/sports/bal-new-paul-heyman-guy-revealed-triple-h-wobbly-on-raw-20130520_1_big-e-langston-extreme-rules-triple-h|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Murphy|first1=Jan|title=Heyman needs no introduction|url=http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Wrestling/2014/08/11/21866561.html|website=[[Canoe.ca|Canoe.ca]]|accessdate=2020-06-12|language=en|archive-date=2015-02-01|archive-url=https://archive.today/20150201134701/http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Wrestling/2014/08/11/21866561.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Shoemaker|first1=David|title=The Mouth of the WWE|url=http://grantland.com/features/wwe-paul-heyman-promo-star-summerslam-brock-lesnar-john-cena|accessdate=2020-06-12|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023229/http://grantland.com/features/wwe-paul-heyman-promo-star-summerslam-brock-lesnar-john-cena/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Hines|first1=Martin|title=WWE and ECW legend Paul Heyman: The Malcolm McLaren of professional wrestling|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/general/wwe-mma-wrestling/paul-heyman-the-malcolm-mclaren-of-professional-wrestling-9639385.html|website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|accessdate=2020-06-12|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612045138/https://www.independent.co.uk/s